Fire story:
The innovator IBM enters into its second century of its existence
We are looking for a suitable word that the strategy of IBM most closely, then this would be the word ' longevity. "
For the general public, IBM is a synonym for technological revolution, it is known as a modern company, although a century has passed since its inception.
The basis for the longevity of her first head - the visionary Thomas J. Watson, H.W.
He argued the slogan, countless worldwide problems could easily be solved if people would be willing to consider a bit.
His slogan: ' Think! " Has been a hallmark of the life of the future giants should happen (and, at the same time, the title of the company's internal magazine, when IBM issued in 1935).
This was also the basis of carefully prepared by Watsen business culture.
" For us, from IBM, this long-term thinking means a kontinuelle movement towards the future.
IBM survived and was also successful in a century, because it has remained true to its principles and not hesitates to change everything else around.
This has enabled us to transform in the course of our first-century technology, business and society.
We hope that we create, " said Samuel J. Palmisano, the director of the company to mark the anniversary in the next hundred years.
Thought-out system
