In many places, apply Saatkrähen: from the cities, the highly intelligent animals no longer drive, say experts, as a "problem of birds."
One, they want to quickly get rid of the other: belong to crow for centuries on the city, but in many municipalities, residents are mounting complaints about dirt and noise of the animals.
It is a tool against the problem of birds, " not yet in sight.
Saatkrähen were not out of the cities, said experts at the first Krähensymposium in ostfriesischen empty.
There consulted experts from across the federal territory on possible ways.
They are looking for alternatives in cities
Conservationists led the problems in towns and cities on the exodus of overprotected Saatkrähen: the use of chemicals in agriculture is increasingly destroyed the traditional habitats.
The hunt, increased building and typical nesting trees made the birds.
Crow are under the protection of nature.
Large colonies, with more than 600 couples nesting there, among other things in the Westphalian Soest, in the north-west, among other things, in Jever, Diepholz and Achim in Bremen and empty.
There was a controversial project in 2005, the mass killing of crow in the district for negative-headlines.
