The project will now have already adopted by tourists.
Also on the criticism of the noise of birds Jürgens had its own opinion: "there is a lot of communication, which have much to say."
The intelligence and skill of the animals are legendary: Saatkrähen use not only tools in order to get a biscuit, but as a tool of their tool even themselves.
Behavioral researchers at Cambridge University recently tested four Saatkrähen, how far does the intelligence of the birds.
