"To play in Costa Rica is a dream to fruition"
In the exclusive interview with Viva says Bassist Jeff Ament of Pearl Jam, the band is prepared to give in the national stadium, one of its best concerts next Sunday.
More than 20 years, they were expected, but the band assured that it is a dream, if they play in Costa Rica.
The Acting Bassist and Mitgründer group, Jeff Ament, Viva last week by Brazil from an exclusive interview.
